category_descriptions.Dehydrated Onion Powder: This category includes ground, pulverized, or powdered dehydrated onions used as a food ingredient or seasoning.
category_descriptions.Dehydrated Onion, Minced or Chopped: This category includes dehydrated onions that have been reduced to small pieces, flakes, or granules.
category_descriptions.Toasted Dehydrated Onion Products: This category includes dehydrated onion products that have undergone a toasting or roasting process.
category_descriptions.Frozen Sliced Onions: This category includes onions that have been sliced and preserved by freezing.
